{"tid":1999991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【五一黃金周】 中國訪港旅客大減　兩日僅 219 人入境","createTime":"2020-05-03T14:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T14:39:05.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa6a19efa4bb4b84c523e8a39b2268a1b1d7836","tid":1999991,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T14:09:49.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情下，今年五一黃金週的內地訪客人數大減，前日（1日）和昨日（2日）合共只有 119 名和 100 名內地訪客入境，比去年單日有過十萬人次入境相距甚遠。<br />\n<br />\n入境處公布 5 月首兩日的出入境人數，當中深圳灣口岸錄得最多出入境人次，1 日和 2 日分別有 110 和 89 名內地訪客經深圳灣入境，56 和 27 名訪客出境。至於其他關口都只有零星內地訪客，兩日合共分別有 10 人經機場入境和出境，而港珠澳大橋合共有 10 人入境和 1 人出境。非內地的海外訪客亦不多，出境人數比入境人次更多，兩日合共有 69 人入境和 175 人出境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%91%A8-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E8%A8%AA%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%9B-%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5%E5%83%85-219-%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25BB%2583%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%2591%25A8-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B8%259B-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2583%2585-219-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%2F&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjguzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=79d3e9de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25BB%2583%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%2591%25A8-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B8%259B-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2583%2585-219-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%2F&h=43d15a04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%91%A8-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E8%A8%AA%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%9B-%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5%E5%83%85-219-%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83/</a